title: The Aldebaran Natzi WWII UFO Connection
description: I like UFO documentaries,I have seen A LOT of them.In my opinion,this is one of the Best for giving you information,and for pure entertainment. This short documentary (39min.) was written,produced,and filmed by Jim Nichols.It deals with Nazi research and development of "flying disc". It also covers "Operation High-jump".Admiral Byrd s mission to the antarctic and the events that may have occurred in January 1947. Additionally,he discusses the current USAF craft and its propulsion system.
